option_values.content: At NN, we are engaged in change on many fronts. This makes our organisation challenging for actuaries and risk specialists like you. Our products and services impact the lives of millions of people worldwide. Therefore, it is important that we carefully weigh our decisions. And that we achieve our ambitions in a controlled and managed way. You make a significant contribution to this by looking at complex issues from different perspectives. And by not only helping to prevent risks but also by seizing  opportunities together. For our customers, for our organization, and for yourself. We are happy to support you bring out the best in yourself.

option_values.content:
As a supporter of change, we are also committed to our own growth and development. This means exciting challenges await you as a tech professional. Did you know that NN is a data- and digitally driven organisation with around 4,000 software engineers, developers, data analysts, and other IT specialists? Our diverse and talented team works collaboratively to drive innovation and shape the future of finance. By leveraging cutting-edge technologies such as OpenAI, GitHub Copilot, and GraphQL, we are creating solutions that not only enhance our services but also redefine what’s possible in the industry.

At NN, we foster a global work environment that celebrates different perspectives and promotes collaboration. You too could be part of this international team, growing alongside our ambitions. By doing so, you'll have the opportunity to make a real difference for more than 20 million customers. With your expertise and skills, you will help people achieve financial security as they navigate life’s milestones — whether that's switching jobs, buying a home, starting a family, or preparing for retirement.
